""SELECT ([t].[FirstName] + N' ') + [t].[LastName] AS [string_var0], [t].[Email] AS [string_var1], [x].[CompanyName] AS [string_var2], [x].[CompanyType] AS [string_var3], [x.Package].[PackageName] AS [string_var4], [x].[ApprovalStatus] AS [string_var6], [x].[CreationTime] AS [date_var0], CONVERT(VARCHAR(36), [x].[Id]) AS [string_var7]
FROM [Company_Registration] AS [x]
LEFT JOIN [Package] AS [x.Package] ON [x].[PackageId] = [x.Package].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [x.User].*
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [x.User]
    WHERE [x.User].[Discriminator] = N'User'

    FROM (
        SELECT TOP(1) [x0].[Id]
        FROM [Company_Registration] AS [x0]
        LEFT JOIN [Package] AS [x.Package0] ON [x0].[PackageId] = [x.Package0].[Id]
        WHERE CONVERT(VARCHAR(36), [x0].[Id]) = @__Id_0
        ORDER BY [x0].[Id]
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.addOnServices].[RegistrationId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
